data.description: Welcome to Salt Creek Landing where nature shouts & commercialization whispers. This beautiful & meticulously maintained home is practically brand new & nestled in a newer gated community on Hilton Head with partial views of the marsh and a day dock! This quaint community is very quiet and boasts views of the marsh & day dock with opportunities for kayaking, fishing, boating, and crabbing. Many upgrades and plenty of flex space underneath the home. Fantastic location, close to restaurants, shopping, and just a short distance to the beach. Easy access to the cross island for travel to Bluffton or anywhere on the island. This is a must see!
